To split changes made to the same file between different commits, in the Commit tool window Alt+0 click Diff.
Select the checkbox next to each chunk of modified or new code that you want to commit and click Commit.
Unselected changes will stay in the current changelist.

为了把某一个文件中所作出的不同改动，分离到不同的commits中。在Commit的工具窗口中，点击 Diff
选择那些你想要提交的、紧挨在修改/新增的代码傍边的checkbox，然后点击Commit
未被选中的改动会被保留在当前的修改列表中。

